data.description:
Seller willing to help with buyer closing costs!

Discover this modern 4BR, 2BA home in Leonor Estates. Boasting contemporary finishes, this home is a testament to stylish, comfortable living. The oversized backyard, landscaped for privacy and relaxation, features an inviting above-ground pool and a Jacuzzi tub, perfect for unwinding.

RV parking adds a layer of convenience, and the proximity to a local park with a basketball court is ideal for family outings and sports lovers. Situated in the SISD school zone, this home promises a quality educational environment.

Only 10 minutes from Eastlake Market Place, you have easy access to shopping and dining. This property offers a blend of modern amenities and serene living, making it an excellent choice for those seeking comfort and convenience in a quiet neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your home.
